{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-03_174", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Lettre meslée de Prose & de Vers de Madame la Viguière d’Alby]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", mars 1678 [tome 3], p. 174-187."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous envoye cependant les Nouvelles galantes & amoureuses qu’on vient de donner au Public. Ce sont diférentes Avantures ramassées dans une Lettre. Vous y trouverez des incidens dont la lecture vous divertira. Je vous donne en mesme temps dequoy en faire une fort agreable, en vous faisant part de ce qui a esté écrit à M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " l’Abbé de la Roque par Madame la Viguiere d’Alby. C’est une Dame d’un fort grand mérite. Tous ceux qui ont leu la Princesse d’Isambourg, que nous avons d’elle, connoissent la force & la délicatesse de son Esprit. Elle s’appelle Madame de Saliez ; & si sa Prose est aisée, on n’a pas moins sujet d’admirer le tour naturel qu’elle donne aux Vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "LETTRE "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "DE MADAME"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[3]", "text": "LA VIGUIERE"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[3]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[4]", "text": "D’ALBY"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[4]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "À Monsieur l’Abbé de la Roque."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous croyez sans-doute, Monsieur, que ce n’est que chez les Ennemis de cet Etat qu’on fait des Conquestes en Hyver, & vous serez surpris d’entendre dire qu’au milieu mesme de la France on ait pris quelque chose dans une si rigoureuse Saison. Cependant, il est certain qu’un jeune Gentilhomme fort brave vient d’y emporter une Place de conséquence, & que faisant feu de tous costez, il l’a réduite à se rendre sous de fort honnestes conditions. Un Amour qui a contribué à cette victoire, en a porté la nouvelle, & voicy comment elle est venuë à ma connoissance."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "J’estois dans ma Chambre resvant sur mes tisons, de cette maniere douce & agreable qui précede toûjours les visions que vous sçavez que les Dieux m’envoyent quelquefois. Les Triomphes infaillibles au Roy dans cette nouvelle Campagne, estoient le sujet de ma resverie, lors que dans ce tranquille état je crûs estre transportée dans un Palais dont les beautez sont au dessus de toutes mes expressions. Celuy d’Armide, ny mesme celuy que l’Amour fit bastir pour Psyché, n’estoient rien en comparaison."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans cette magnifique Place,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Entre le Ciel & le Parnasse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "La Déesse Vénus dans ses brillans atours,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Reçoit de temps en temps l’hommage des Amours."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Là, sans déguisement, sans art, sans imposture,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Chacun luy dit son Avanture,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Et l’on y voit les Amours fortunez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Par ses belles mains couronnez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Recevoir des Leçons de l’aimable Déesse ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour augmenter leur joye & leur tendresse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle donne courage aux Amours malheureux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle prend soin de les instruire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Et soûtient par ces soins tout l’Empire amoureux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Que la Raison voudroit détruire."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Une nuit que le Ciel éclairoit foiblement,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Vénus tenoit son Assemblée,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout s’y passoit tranquilement ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand soudain elle fut troublée."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Un Amour qui n’aguere estoit pâsle & réveur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Dont mille ennuis troubloient le cœur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Par de grands cris se faisoit faire place ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "On lisoit sur son front sa joye & son audace."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Déesse, disoit-il, des plus vaillans Guerriers"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[24]/text()[1]", "text": "J’efface aujourd’huy la Victoire ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[25]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[25]/text()[1]", "text": "Faites que mille Amours en admirant ma gloire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[26]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[26]/text()[1]", "text": "Me viennent couronner de Mirthe & de Lauriers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[27]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[27]/text()[1]", "text": "Cette Place si forte & si bien défenduë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[28]/text()[1]", "text": "Que tant d’Amour assiegeoient vainement,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[29]/text()[1]", "text": "Par mon adresse s’est renduë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[30]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[30]/text()[1]", "text": "Et la charmante Iris rend heureux son Amant."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces derniers mots me surprirent fort. Comme j’avois l’esprit occupé des Conquestes qui sont si ordinaires au Roy, je croyois qu’on alloit parler de la prise de quelque Ville de Flandre ou d’Alsace ; mais tandis que je me reprochois mon erreur, cet Amour continuoit ainsy."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce n’est point par des artifices,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "chil